verbose_text: To further confirm the link between AHNAK2 expression and metabolic shifting in ccRCC, we measured expression levels of the genes related to fatty acid and lipid synthesis in CAKI-1 and 786-O cells after knockdown of AHNAK2, including ATP citrate lyase (ACLY), acetyl-CoA carboxylase (ACC), fatty acid synthase (FASN), stearoyl-CoA Desaturase-1 (SCD1) and so on.
